  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.Controller

    public class SsoDestroyingServiceValidateController
extends org.jasig.cas.web.ServiceValidateController
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
    An extention of a ServiceValidateController that destroys server-side TGT upon successful Service Ticket validation.

    Useful for services that are configured not to initiate WebSSO sessions altogether.

    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Dmitriy Kopylenko,, Unicon, inc.
